cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR, cs.MM. 

The paper deals with a machine learning-based approach for single image intrinsic decomposition, which is a computer vision problem. Therefore, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also proposes a new loss function and uses a deep convolutional neural network, which falls under the sub-categories of cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also introduces a new dataset and proposes quantitative metrics, which could fall under cs.GR (Graphics) and cs.MM (Multimedia).
